Bitmain Technologies Ltd., or Bitmain,[1] is a privately-owned multi-national semiconductor company headquartered in Beijing, China. They are a leading producer and designer of ASIC chips which are used for bitcoin mining and Artificial Intelligence.
In addition to ASIC chip development, the company is the world's largest producer of specialist hardware built for cryptocurrency mining, which they sell to consumers under the "AntMiner" brand and operates Antpool, historically one of the largest bitcoin mining pools.
